@UserService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5002

### Send OTP
POST {{UserService_HostAddress}}/api/users/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "countryCode": "+91"
}

###

### Verify OTP without device info
POST {{UserService_HostAddress}}/api/users/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "countryCode": "+91",
  "otp": "1234"
}

###

### Verify OTP with device info
POST {{UserService_HostAddress}}/api/users/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "countryCode": "+91",
  "otp": "1234",
  "fcmToken": "fcm_token_here",
  "deviceId": "device_12345",
  "deviceType": "android"
}

###
